{
  "stem": "16106.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did-- they did-- I didn't have the uniform anymore, not my clogs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had stockings and things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, those people took good care of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took very good care for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] OK, then-- then I got in the car, and Fraulein Veronica [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Reimer ?] got the job with Organisation Todt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got assigned an apartment, had to appear in an office every morning and say, heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was not much to do, because it was over for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, it was just pushing the papers and the pen back and forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was all a big show for nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I do remember Hitler's birthday, his last.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was, I think, the 8th of-- it was in April-- April the 15-- April something, Hitler's birthday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had to come all down there and say heil Hitler, and all those lovely thing one says.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the other thing, which was-- which very interesting was that I, as a German woman, was-- had access to radio and news.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The others were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were lots of Polish [GERMAN] and Russian [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They have always those-- they had everything compartmentalized there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was a [GERMAN], that was not a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was the only true German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] [INAUDIBLE] I always have to think that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I got to listen to the radio, and I know that the Russians are here, and the Americans are there, and here's a freed camp, and there's a freed camp, and there is little Shoshama Rose in-- in the middle with the Germans, and cannot budge.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did anyone know your true identity?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I know of.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
